summary: I just finished this drawing of Ikki from Air Gear. I have been rereading air gear one of my favorite manga. The art and style...
caption:
I just finished this drawing of Ikki from Air Gear. I have been rereading air gear one of my favorite manga. The art and style of this series are amazing which made this a blast to draw. I love rollerblading and the manga combining it with the idea of flight with the incredible art style makes it an instant read.

I plan on coloring this in photoshop, and with Copic markers so look forward to that!
